{"tid":2334133,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"印度神童又預言成功，武漢肺炎變種","createTime":"2020-12-21T03:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T03:59:43.000Z","uid":249170,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d16cfd6f08f981ecc9688529ac2d96953b58ab96","tid":2334133,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"仲要咁多人移民左去英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國出現新型冠狀病毒變種，傳播速度快七成，有歐洲國家出現變種病毒引起的個案，歐洲多國停飛往返英國的航班，連接英國同歐洲的歐洲之星高速火車接近停運。<br />\n<br />\n德國、意大利，荷蘭、比利時、奧地利及愛爾蘭先後宣布暫停往返英國的航班。<br />\n<br />\n法國暫時禁止來自英國的航班、列車和輪渡運入境48小時。英國多佛港渡輪碼頭關閉。加拿大亦宣布停飛自英國的航班。<br />\n<br />\n捷克表示會加強英國旅客的檢疫措施。以色列政府將禁止英國，丹麥和南非航班入境。<br />\n<br />\n英國衛生大臣夏國賢表示，變種病毒已經失控，必須加以控制。首相約翰遜星期一將召開緊急應變會議商討對策。<br />\n<br />\n美國高級衛生官員表示，正非常謹慎地研究英國的病毒變，同時指出目前沒有禁止英國旅客的計劃。官員又相信疫苗對變種病毒仍有保護力。"},{"pid":"a7194e01448037f9b119f7700eb45a498dd6f5ef","tid":2334133,"uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:23:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nigel_farage/status/1340342881521971206?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnigel_farage%2Fstatus%2F1340342881521971206%3Fs%3D21&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=29520540\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnigel_farage%2Fstatus%2F1340342881521971206%3Fs%3D21&h=418a9938\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nigel_farage/status/1340342881521971206?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"a4b5a75d2eea9b111086209aec6cdf466d62d626","tid":2334133,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7194e01448037f9b119f7700eb45a498dd6f5ef","tid":2334133,"uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:23:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nigel_farage/status/1340342881521971206?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft